      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLACK DAZZLER (3) box seated off the lead and kept coming to win (17.39) at this track in Maiden over 300m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program in her latest win. Can go close again if runs up to latest figure. ZIPPING SINNER (2) made a big impression on debut when used the inside draw to advantage and hit the ground running with a fast early split, paving the way for a 4 length win at this track over 300m in 17.49. Shows good promise and should be in this for a long way. JUST TAKE IT (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind ZIPPING SINNER (17.75) in a Maiden. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Expected to feature. URBAN TIGER (7) makes debut for the Scott Tyson kennel. Start all important and will need some luck getting across from the wide draw. Profiles nicely but market best guide to ability.",
